{"tid":818612,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【月經】一人一個惡頂見工經驗","createTime":"2018-09-14T08:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T09:33:40.000Z","uid":69083,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"336281f6b23b40334eb24b752aa3443cf8a3a84f","tid":818612,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:26:23.000Z","msg":"小弟30分鐘見咗份惡頂MT工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仆你個街間公司office係中環d垃圾後巷<br />\n間公司又舊又細又霉<br />\n<br />\n一開波英文自我介紹, 講到唔夠一半佢要禁電話做公司野, okay, 大家都忙都明白嘅<br />\n等佢覆完個msg就重新多次自我介紹<br />\n接著就蝗語講讀書嘅野, 都okay<br />\n<br />\n到問有咩優點可以勝任呢個MT, 咪講我係以前公司點點點做到野, 佢開始黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無啦啦屌鳩我講野似保險佬, 自吹自擂, 我心諗有邊個見工唔係吹水架。<br />\n又屌鳩我講野唔到point<br />\n又唔可以講「唔得」<br />\n又唔可以反問<br />\n又屈鳩我條氣唔順佢禁電話<br />\n又唔俾解釋, 佢即刻「NoNoNo」你<br />\n又話其實我測試你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌那星  佢以為玩緊SM女僕, 佢差在未叫我稱呼佢「HR腥些沙媽」咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見佢咁唔鍾意俾人解釋, 費撚事哂時間, 係佢面前撕撚爛張application form, 臨走前講咗佢「NoNoNoNoNo...」"},{"pid":"ab6968d3631ef6202b78d4fb3f329524b82723c1","tid":818612,"uid":171594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"如果係真，真心佩服你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8445dd094734feb880c6fe95ffd2dd1c5e8d38","tid":818612,"uid":196459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"有次見工 全職<br />\n見完 佢都好滿意<br />\n不過佢話:<br />\n我地依家無fulltime既位,只可以offer parttime比你<br />\n一星期番5日朝早<br />\n你做唔做呀?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2270aa05c614d6db8daa27af5bb5d6c5ecb3435","tid":818612,"uid":124859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:38:23.000Z","msg":"好型呀<br />